<p>In this installment we talk about how microservices live in a <a href="http://martinfowler.com/articles/microservices.html#DecentralizedGovernance">world of decentralized governance</a>. Rather than having a governance group define standards for services, services make their own decisions and are encouraged to share common solutions. With this installment we also look at the <a href="http://martinfowler.com/articles/microservices.html#MicroservicesAndSoa">relationship between microservices and SOA</a>.</p>
